genresAdvancedInfo.name: metal nortista
genresAdvancedInfo.description: A style of heavy metal that originated in northern Brazil. It combines traditional Brazilian rhythms with elements of heavy metal, creating a unique blend of music that is both energetic and infectious. The lyrics often touch on themes of social justice, politics, and the struggles of everyday life. The music is characterized by its use of percussion instruments, fast-paced guitar riffs, and catchy melodies.
